
@startuml

class Cinema {
  - name: String
  - address: String
  - copies: Set<MovieCopy>
}

class Theatre {
  - name: String
  - cinema: Cinema
  - seats: Integer
}

class Movie {
  - title: String
  - duration: Integer
}

class MovieCopy {
  - id: String
  - movie: Movie
  - cinema: Cinema
  - currentTheatre: Theatre
}

class Show {
  - id: String
  - startTime: DateTime
  - endTime: DateTime
  - movieCopy: MovieCopy
  - theatre: Theatre
  - isPublished: Boolean
}

class Reservation {
  - id: String
  - show: Show
  - customer: Customer
  - seatNumber: Integer
  - isCancelled: Boolean
  - reservationTime: DateTime
}

class Offer {
  - id: String
  - show: Show
  - newShow: Show
  - offerTime: DateTime
  - expirationTime: DateTime
  - status: Enum("Pending", "Accepted", "Declined", "Expired")
}

class Customer {
  - id: String
  - name: String
  - email: String
  - creditCard: CreditCard
}

class CreditCard {
  - cardNumber: String
  - expiryDate: Date
  - cvv: String
}

class Ticket {
  - id: String
  - show: Show
  - customer: Customer
  - seatNumber: Integer
  - isAnonymous: Boolean
  - isRefundable: Boolean
}

' Associations

Cinema "1" -- "0..*" Cinema : has
Cinema "1" -- "1..*" Theatre : has
Theatre "1" -- "1" MovieCopy : uses
Movie "1" -- "0..*" MovieCopy : has
MovieCopy "1" -- "1" Show : has
Show "1" -- "0..*" Reservation : has
Show "1" -- "0..*" Offer : can offer
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Reservation : makes
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Ticket : buys
Show "1" -- "0..*" Ticket : has
Ticket "1" -- "1" Show : belongs to

@enduml

### Explanation of Key Relationships:
- A **Cinema** owns multiple **Theatres**, and each **Theatre** has a certain number of **seats**.
- A **MovieCopy** is tied to a specific **Movie** and located in a **Cinema**. It can be moved between theatres.
- A **Show** is associated with one **MovieCopy** and takes place in a specific **Theatre**.
- A **Reservation** is made by a **Customer** for a specific **Show** and includes a **seat number**.
- If a **Show** is cancelled, an **Offer** may be created for another **Show** (same movie, different theatre).
- **Tickets** can be issued either via **online reservations** or at the **ticketing desk**, and they are assigned a **seat number**.

